, That where the needed equipment costs more than five thousand pesos per unit, and the same is procurable only from a sole dealer, distributor or importer, or other source, the purchase thereof by the city without public bidding is also hereby authorized:

Provided

, That the price to be paid therefor is approved by the City Committee on Award created under Republic Act Numbered Twenty-Two Hundred and sixty-four, and certified by the Bureau of Supply Coordination as the lowest and most advantageous to the city;

